              <span id="reviewTextContainer2063811257" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1636770855448200748">Pretty darn good and highly suspenseful. I recommend this one if you&apos;re in the mood for a super-quick suspense read! It&apos;s over in a snap and you&apos;re left wondering what horror might have awaited the old couple had the man not made the last wish. Spooky. </span>
  <span id="freeText1636770855448200748" style="display:none">Pretty darn good and highly suspenseful. I recommend this one if you're in the mood for a super-quick suspense read! It's over in a snap and you're left wondering what horror might have awaited the old couple had the man not made the last wish. Spooky. </span>
